00:16:24.619 --> 00:16:28.099
with better sacrifices than these.

00:16:28.099 --> 00:16:30.899
For Christ is not entered into the holy places

00:16:30.899 --> 00:16:32.539
made with hands,

00:16:32.539 --> 00:16:36.339
which are the figures of the true,

00:16:36.339 --> 00:16:38.139
but into heaven itself,

00:16:38.139 --> 00:16:42.059
now to appear in the presence of God for us.

00:16:42.099 --> 00:16:45.019
For yet, that He should offer Himself often

00:16:45.019 --> 00:16:47.139
as the high priest entereth into the holy place

00:16:47.139 --> 00:16:49.779
every year with blood of others.

00:16:49.779 --> 00:16:52.819
For then must He often have suffered

00:16:52.819 --> 00:16:54.939
since the foundation of the world.

00:16:54.939 --> 00:16:56.500
But now once in the end of the world

00:16:56.500 --> 00:16:58.859
hath He appeared to put away sin

00:16:58.859 --> 00:17:02.219
by the sacrifice of Himself.

