We find in the book of Philippians

00:17:55.659 --> 00:17:58.419
in chapter 2, beginning in verse 5,

00:17:58.419 --> 00:17:59.259
the Bible says,

00:17:59.259 --> 00:18:00.299
let this mind be in you,

00:18:00.299 --> 00:18:02.579
which was also in Christ Jesus,

00:18:02.579 --> 00:18:03.939
