00:18:06.059 --> 00:18:07.779
Why? Because He is God.

00:18:07.779 --> 00:18:08.419
Verse 7,

00:18:08.419 --> 00:18:11.059
But made Himself of no reputation

00:18:11.059 --> 00:18:13.139
and took upon Him the form of a servant,

00:18:13.139 --> 00:18:14.659
was made in the likeness of men.

00:18:14.659 --> 00:18:15.699
Notice verse 8,

00:18:15.699 --> 00:18:17.619
